* Dinobot eyed Tavatron again before he looked back to the screen and looked 
at the name that she was pointing to, the name seemed familiar but it was 
spelled and sounded slightly different. He looked over the name then 
scrolled the computer quickly down and scanned the information, to anybot 
else the screen was nothing but a blur but to Dinobot it was as clear as 
day.
By the time that he was through scanning and stopped scrolling the computer 
screen was on a completely other name.
Dinobot sat back in his chair and tapped his claw on the table in thought, 
so this was proving as not such a waste in time as he had thought.
He growled as his systems replayed the information back on his internal 
screen, he looked over it and came to a conclusion.*

" This...Transanulas is neither, Neutral. He was cloned off of the Predacon 
soldier Tarantulus and now exists as an oppertunist. He uses bots and 
disposes of them when their talents are no longer useful."
